	<body>
		<header>
			'There is' or 'there are'?  Look at the picture and fill the gaps.
		</header>
		
		<section id="body">
			<img class="rightFloat" src="media/fishnchips.png" />
			
			<p class="padLeft">
				<b>x'There is' or 'There are'?</b>
			</p>
			
			<p>
				We use <g class="blue">There is...</g> with uncountable nouns and countable singular nouns.  We use <g class="blue">There are...</g> with countable
				plural nouns.  For example:<br/>
				<g class="blue">There is a cat on the table!</g><br/>
				<g class="blue">There is some ice in this drink.</g><br/>
				<g class="blue">There are two cats on the table!</g><br/>
			</p>
			
